    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>John Gruber <a href="http://www.macworld.com/article/2018607/the-unlikely-persistence-of-applescript.html">for Macworld</a>:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>…AppleScript allows me to add my <em>own</em> features to the apps I use most—features that may well not make sense for the typical user but which save me time and aggravation.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Nice little history of one of my favorite aspects of OS X.</p>

